            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Memorial of Maurus, seller of goat meat</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Transcribed by Schubring in materials sent to the Berlin academy in October 1865 (his no.219; now in the CIL archives), but no details of provenance are recorded. Ferrua proposed reading 'caprinarius' in the final line, accepted by both Rizzo and Chioffi.</p>
